name: Buy The Ticket...
description: This was taken near Yosemite in 2012. This man tried to charge me for taking the photo. I gave him $20 dollars after he made the case that his bus was art. He told me he was the last honest man in the world. We had a laugh. To date, this is the most expensive photo I've taken. Therefore, it's my first mint, and free. I will burn remains at some point.
